em. We outline how to implement more effective background rejection\ntechniques using this information. Reducing backgrounds in solar and DSNB\nstudies by even a factor of a few could help lead to important new discoveries.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 19 Feb 2014 15:12:11 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 3 Mar 2014 00:31:43 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 13 Apr 2014 21:30:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-04-23"}
